Titolo: Alfred Hitchcock – Vertigo

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Alfred Hitchcock – Vertigo is an adventure video game developed by the Spanish company Pendulo Studios and published by Microids. It is loosely based on the films of Alfred Hitchcock, particularly Vertigo. The story follows a man named Ed Miller, who enters therapy to cope with the mysterious after-effects of a car crash. 
Pendulo and Microids announced Vertigo in early 2018, during the development of their game Blacksad: Under the Skin. It was first shown at the Guerrilla Collective Showcase in June 2021. The game was released on Windows in December 2021, and is planned for game consoles in 2022.